{"text_id":26046,"tokens":["##"," Poly","archy","\n\n","**","Poly","archy","**"," is"," a"," form"," of"," government"," that"," simultaneously"," emphasizes"," both"," democracy"," and"," olig","archy","."," The"," term"," originates"," from"," the"," Greek"," words"," \"","pol","ys","\""," (","meaning"," \"","many","\")"," and"," \"","arch","\u0113","\""," (","meaning"," \"","rule","\")."," Unlike"," a"," pure"," democracy",","," where"," all"," citizens"," directly"," participate"," in"," decision","-","making",","," or"," a"," pure"," olig","archy",","," where"," power"," is"," concentrated"," in"," the"," hands"," of"," a"," small"," group",","," poly","archy"," blends"," elements"," of"," both",".","\n\n","**","Characteristics",":**","\n\n","*"," **","Limited"," Suff","rage",":**"," While"," poly","arch","ies"," feature"," some"," form"," of"," universal"," suffrage",","," it"," may"," be"," restricted"," in"," certain"," areas"," or"," for"," specific"," types"," of"," decisions",".","  ","\n","*"," **","E","lected"," Representative"," Assemblies",":**"," Citizens"," elect"," representatives"," to"," make"," decisions"," on"," their"," behalf","."," These"," assemblies"," typically"," possess"," significant"," power",","," but"," their"," composition"," and"," powers"," might"," be"," influenced"," by"," factors"," beyond"," simple"," majority"," rule",".","\n","*"," **","Plural","ism",":**"," Multiple"," political"," parties",","," interest"," groups",","," and"," factions"," exist"," and"," compete"," for"," influence","."," ","\n","*"," **","Limited"," Checks"," &"," Bal","ances",":**"," While"," checks"," and"," balances"," exist",","," they"," may"," be"," weaker"," than"," in"," fully"," democratic"," systems",".","\n\n","**","Variations",":**","\n\n","Different"," forms"," of"," poly","archy"," can"," exist",","," depending"," on"," the"," specific"," distribution"," of"," power"," and"," influence","."," ","\n\n","*"," **","Competitive"," Poly","archy",":**"," This"," type"," emphasizes"," open"," political"," competition"," between"," different"," parties"," and"," groups",".","  ","While"," power"," may"," not"," be"," evenly"," distributed",","," there","'","s"," regular"," turnover"," between"," different"," factions",".","\n","*"," **","Eli","tist"," Poly","archy",":**"," Resources"," and"," influence"," are"," more"," concentrated"," among"," a"," smaller",","," privileged"," group","."," Election"," outcomes"," might"," appear"," democratic",","," but"," the"," influence"," of"," the"," elite"," shapes"," policy"," outcomes",".","\n\n","**","Examples",":**","\n\n","Historically",","," some"," historians"," and"," political"," scientists"," argue"," that"," certain"," historical"," regimes",","," such"," as"," the"," Roman"," Republic"," or"," the"," early"," Florentine"," Republic",","," exhibited"," poly","arch","al"," characteristics",".","\n\n","**","Contemporary"," Debate",":**","\n\n","The"," concept"," of"," poly","archy"," is"," debated"," within"," political"," science","."," Critics"," argue"," that"," it","'","s"," a"," misleading"," term"," as"," it"," attempts"," to"," reconcile"," inherent"," tensions"," between"," democracy"," and"," olig","archy","."," They"," contend"," that"," genuine"," democracy"," requires"," more"," robust"," citizen"," participation"," and"," checks"," on"," power",".","\n\n","**","Further"," Reading",":**","\n\n","*"," Dahl",","," Robert"," A","."," (","1","9","7","1",")."," *","Poly","archy",":"," Participation"," and"," Opposition","*."],"sub_source":"wikipedia","model":"gemma2-9b-it","label":1}